fields.label: Description of Current Financial Situation
I certify that I currently have no income from any source.
fields.options:
Zero Income Self-Certification

Please complete this section only if no adult in your household has income.

I certify that as of today, neither I nor any adult member of my household currently receives income from:

  • Employment (full-time, part-time, temporary, or self-employment)
  • Unemployment benefits, Social Security, disability benefits, pensions, or retirement accounts
  • Child support, spousal support, or regular cash support from family or friends
  • Rental income, investments, or any other ongoing source of income

If I receive any benefits or supports (for example: SNAP/food benefits, TANF, SSI/SSDI, other assistance), I have listed them here:

How I am meeting basic needs

Please explain how you are currently meeting basic needs such as food, housing, and utilities (for example: staying with family/friends, community support, benefits, etc.):

Certification

By signing or submitting this form, I certify that the information I have provided about my income is true and complete to the best of my knowledge. I understand that giving false or misleading information may affect my eligibility for services or assistance.
